data.name: Well child visit
data.description: A regular check-up that is typically scheduled every few months up until age 2 and annually thereafter.

data.name: Acute care visit
data.description: A visit to address new symptoms like cough, cold, ear pain, fever, diarrhea, or rash.

data.name: Follow up visit
data.long_description: A visit to follow up on a known condition like asthma, ADHD, or eczema.

data.name: Immunization visit
data.description: A visit with a nurse to get one or more immunizations.
